verbose_text: Among the 43 genes that were differentially expressed between the senescent fibroblasts and controls, 4 encoded secreted proteins : senescent fibroblasts expressed higher levels of LIF1 and lower levels of COL5A3, APOL6 and SDF1 than were observed in normal fibroblasts.
